name: UNCEASING VIXEN 14:13
description: Her blanket fell to the floor, so she curled up to keep warm. The rain pounds the window above her head. A half-empty glass of vino sits on the table beside the chair. In her, I search for my anima, but all I can see is an unceasing vixen. Her innocence only compounds her seductiveness. Only the two of us exist here, but I get chills from her loving shill. I lurk from across the room like an adolescent seeing his first naked lady. It’s exciting, beautiful, pure, and terrifying at the same time. My sexual imagination has left me in a trance from which I may never awaken.
